        in 'read.table'. It allows to write (small)
        inline tables as in

          data <- readOrg(text =
          "
          |       when | amount |
          |------------+--------|
          | 2016-01-01 |     -1 |
          | 2016-02-01 |      2 |
          | 2016-03-01 |     -2 |
          "

